<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:48px;font-size:.93rem;line-height:1.85;color:#374151">

      <p style="color:var(--gray);font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:32px">This agreement is between <strong>Sites by Mel</strong> ("Mel", "we", "us") and you, the customer ("you", "client"), and applies to all website design services purchased at sitesbymel.com. By submitting your intake form, you confirm you have read and agree to these terms.</p>

      <!-- 1 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">1. Scope of Work</h2>
      <p>Each purchase covers one (1) personalized, 5-page HTML website built from a Sites by Mel template. The five pages are: Home, About, Services (or equivalent), Gallery/Portfolio, and Contact. The finished website files are delivered as a downloadable ZIP package.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Work included in your purchase:</p>
      <ul style="margin:10px 0 10px 20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
        <li>Replacing placeholder text with your submitted business information</li>
        <li>Placing your uploaded photos in the appropriate spots on the template</li>
        <li>Updating contact details, tagline, services, and hours throughout all pages</li>
        <li>A final mobile and desktop review before delivery</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Work <strong>not</strong> included unless you purchased a specific add-on: domain registration, DNS configuration, email setup, hosting, copywriting, or custom design changes outside the template structure.</p>

      <!-- 2 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">2. Your Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>To complete your website, Mel needs accurate information from you. By submitting the intake form, you confirm:</p>
      <ul style="margin:10px 0 10px 20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
        <li>All business information you provide (name, address, phone, email, services, hours) is accurate and belongs to your business</li>
        <li>You own or have the legal right to use any photos, logos, or other content you upload</li>
        <li>You will respond to any follow-up questions from Mel within 5 business days — delays on your end may delay delivery</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">If you checked <strong>"Let Mel Handle This"</strong> on any field or photo slot, you are authorizing Mel to write copy or select stock photography on your behalf. You agree to review this content at delivery and understand that AI-assisted writing may be used.</p>

      <!-- 3 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">3. Revisions</h2>
      <p>Your purchase includes <strong>one (1) round of revisions</strong> — meaning one set of changes submitted together after delivery. Revisions are limited to corrections of submitted information (a typo in your phone number, a wrong service name, etc.) and minor text edits.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Revisions do <strong>not</strong> include: redesigning the template layout, changing the template to a different niche, adding pages, or rebuilding sections. Those requests are quoted separately. Additional revision rounds beyond the first are $25 each.</p>

      <!-- 4 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">4. Delivery Timeline</h2>
      <p>Mel aims to deliver your completed website within <strong>48 hours</strong> of receiving your completed intake form during normal business hours (Monday–Friday). Complex orders, missing information, or high order volume may extend this timeline. You will receive an email at delivery with your download link.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Your download link is valid for <strong>7 days</strong> from delivery. If your link expires before you download, contact mel@sitesbymel.com and a new link will be provided.</p>

      <!-- 5 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">5. Domains &amp; Hosting</h2>
      <p>Unless you purchased the Domain Setup ($499) or Template Launch ($797) package, your purchase does <strong>not</strong> include a domain name or web hosting. You are responsible for purchasing your own domain (typically $10–$15/year from registrars like Namecheap or GoDaddy) and choosing a hosting provider.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Your completed ZIP file can be deployed to free hosting platforms such as Netlify Drop (app.netlify.com/drop) at no cost. Mel is happy to answer basic questions about hosting via email but is not responsible for hosting setup under the Template Package.</p>

      <!-- 6 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">6. Ownership &amp; Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>Upon full payment and delivery, <strong>you own your finished website files</strong> — the HTML, CSS, and any content you provided. You may host, edit, and distribute them freely. No monthly license or platform fee is required to use your files.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Mel retains ownership of the underlying template design and structure. This means Mel may continue selling the same base template to other customers. Your ownership covers the personalized version with your specific content — not the template framework itself.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Stock photos selected by Mel on your behalf are licensed for web use under the Unsplash License (unsplash.com/license). You may use them on your website but may not resell the photos as standalone assets.</p>

      <!-- 7 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">7. Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>Because website work begins immediately after your intake form is submitted, <strong>refunds are not available once work has started</strong>.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">If you contact Mel before submitting your intake form, a full refund will be issued. If Mel is unable to complete your order due to circumstances on our end, a full refund will be issued. If your delivered website has errors caused by our mistake (not by information you provided incorrectly), Mel will correct them at no charge.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">If you are unhappy with your delivery, please email mel@sitesbymel.com before requesting a chargeback. Mel is committed to making it right.</p>

      <!-- 8 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Sites by Mel is not liable for any lost revenue, missed opportunities, or business losses arising from delays in delivery, errors in the delivered website, or your inability to launch your site on time. Our total liability in any dispute is limited to the amount you paid for your order.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px">Mel is not responsible for third-party services including domain registrars, hosting providers, Stripe, Netlify, or email providers.</p>

      <!-- 9 -->
      <h2 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);margin:32px 0 10px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">9. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By checking the agreement checkbox on the intake form and clicking Submit, you confirm that:</p>
      <ul style="margin:10px 0 10px 20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
        <li>You have read and understood this agreement</li>
        <li>You are 18 years of age or older, or have parental/guardian consent</li>
        <li>You authorize Sites by Mel to begin work on your website using the information you provided</li>
        <li>You agree to pay any outstanding balance before final delivery where applicable</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #86efac;border-radius:8px;padding:20px 24px;margin-top:32px">
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:#166534;margin:0"><strong>Questions?</strong> Email <a href="mailto:mel@sitesbymel.com" style="color:#166534">mel@sitesbymel.com</a> before submitting your order. Mel is happy to clarify anything in this agreement.</p>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gray);margin-top:32px;text-align:center">Last updated: June 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Sites by Mel &nbsp;·&nbsp; sitesbymel.com</p>
